window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Experience one of television's greatest science-fiction series: <i>The Twilight Zone</i> - fully dramatized for audio! Featuring a full cast, music and sound effects, and today's biggest celebrities in modern radio dramatizations. </p> <p>Ever since he came back to life at his own funeral, Jeff Myrtlebank just hasn't been the same. The townspeople want to run him out of town, because they think he might be possessed by demons, but Jeff says they have no reason to fear him.</p>"; 
